folder: Ave. U & Stuart St., Brooklyn, NY
text:
(1)
3116-3124 Ave. U., at the S.W. corner of Stuart Street, showing a home used as a club by the Whitneys in 1900. In 1926 it was rebuilt and known as the Club Whitney, a bootleg liquor establishment. In 1929 it was the Marine Park Inn.

May 1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The same, at a later date.

August 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

text:
